WEBVTT

00:08:59.248 --> 00:09:01.488
osjetili pijesak pod nogama,

00:09:01.512 --> 00:09:02.663
krenuli prema obali,

00:09:02.687 --> 00:09:04.800
i pustili da vam gležnjeve
zapljuskuje more.

00:09:05.207 --> 00:09:08.022
Život će vam biti bogatiji i smisleniji

00:09:08.046 --> 00:09:10.264
jer doslovno udišete to iskustvo,

00:09:10.288 --> 00:09:12.684
a sve zato što ste
ostavili telefon u autu.

00:09:12.708 --> 00:09:13.879
Hvala.

00:09:13.903 --> 00:09:16.204
(Pljesak)